Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.73,0:00:05.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,I am Hanako
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.56,0:00:07.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,You are my friend
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.82,0:00:09.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,He is a teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:11.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,You are my friend
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.32,0:00:17.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.79,0:00:26.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.13,0:00:28.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:33.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我没…干什么呀
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——op——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:12.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,橡皮擦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.19,0:02:17.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这弹簧不错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:25.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只要把它装进去 吓人盒子就做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:30.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,给我瞧好了 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:37.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:41.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我打不开文具盒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:43.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,会不会是掉在地上的时候摔坏了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.77,0:02:46.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.21,0:02:47.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,帮我开一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.98,0:02:50.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:02:58.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么嘛 一下子就打开了嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:07.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片 你搞什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:11.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,对不起 什么事也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:26.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片的反应真的很有趣呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:31.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要…要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:37.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:40.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,完全被耍了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:44.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,而且还把我想要做的事给抢先一步…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:50.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,本来高木同学来找我帮忙就很可疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:52.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我竟然没有察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:55.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,得想想下一招了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:04:00.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是要怎么做才能捉弄到高木同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:11.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:15.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:17.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,借我橡皮擦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:19.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我忘带了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:35.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,连橡皮擦都能忘带 你真笨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:38.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是啊 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:53.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:57.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,传闻要是在橡皮上写下喜欢的人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:05:01.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,当橡皮擦用完的时候两个人就会两情相悦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:05.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,还真有那回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:08.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,现在想起来 还真是幼稚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:14.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,幼稚…啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:30.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:47.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,到底怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:56.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,上面什么也没写吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:06:00.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我…才不会做那么幼稚的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:05.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,呵呵 是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:09.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这是假的 你一定又在捉弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:13.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:14.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我写了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.27,0:06:16.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我在上面写了东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:19.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,难道只是我忘记了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:28.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,快点还给我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:32.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:37.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是这样的 肯定是别人写上去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:44.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明明什么都没有写啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.26,0:06:48.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,话说 高木同学不是带了橡皮擦嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:50.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:52.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:55.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:07:00.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,手忙脚乱的 还挨骂了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.57,0:07:06.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的 你好歹注意一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:08.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这是我要说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:12.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,老师 我可以去上厕所吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:13.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:23.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,难道就没有什么能让高木同学难为情的方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:29.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:33.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,趁现在在高木同学的橡皮上面随便写上某个人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:36.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等她从厕所回来 就好好捉弄一下她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:40.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那么 要写谁的名字呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.11,0:07:45.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,橡皮上面已经有字了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.12,0:07:52.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看到了的话会很糟糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:55.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不过只看一个字的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:07:59.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,Ro？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:02.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是Ro的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:11.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就不是…我的名字了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:17.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,其实我也不是受打击了什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:34.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:38.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我…我要看了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:43.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样的话 干脆全看了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:46.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:49.05,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\move(1044,926,1042,872,0,2487)}看\N走\N廊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:49.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs40}注：日语中「走廊」的第一个字是Ro
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:09:00.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,中 中计了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:09.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片的表情真的很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:14.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,而且还会按我预料的那样做出反应
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.37,0:09:21.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以我才会忍不住想要捉弄你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:24.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你给我看好了 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:29.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,总有一天 我要捉弄你 让你出丑的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:31.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我很期待喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:34.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你一定是觉得我办不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:35.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:38.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我认真的 你给我等着瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:41.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我觉得是白费功夫喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:44.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你可是让二分之一的大好机会溜走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:47.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么 二分之一？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:48.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:50.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:54.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,值日好麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:03.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么非要提早去擦黑板写日志不可呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:07.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,值日真是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:10.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早起的鸟儿有虫吃果然有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:15.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这不是游戏厅的代币吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:21.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,值日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:28.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,对了 不如趁这个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:31.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在高木同学的桌子上搞点恶作剧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:35.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,困意减了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:50.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学已经来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:52.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:10:59.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没有人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:03.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真奇怪啊 是我看错了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:08.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 我能感受到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:10.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是高木同学的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.15,0:11:13.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,肯定是藏到哪里去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.07,0:11:17.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好险 虽然只有一小会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:19.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我竟然放松警惕差点哼起小曲来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:22.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她在哪儿 她藏到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:31.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,天真 太天真了 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:34.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,透过间隙 你的鞋子被我看得一清二楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:39.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你是想趁我上去擦黑板的时候吓唬我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.22,0:11:41.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不过我可不会上当
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.60,0:11:47.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,值日太麻烦了 我还是不做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:50.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,黑板就算不擦也不会被发现啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:52.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么样啊 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:57.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,阴谋诡计被揭穿了 一定很懊恼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:02.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哎呀 真想看看高木同学懊悔的样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:04.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:06.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,暴露自己的鞋子什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:08.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学会犯这种低级错误吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:12.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 她不会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:14.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,也就是说那是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:17.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:19.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真不愧是高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:23.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那么 本尊藏到哪里去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.18,0:12:28.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,毕竟是高木同学 她肯定会留在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:35.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看上去不像是在走廊上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:37.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那么 剩下的就只有…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:44.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊啊 去上厕所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:48.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看我吓你一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:52.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:58.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:19.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我究竟在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:32.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:35.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,竟然藏在窗帘后面…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:37.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没想到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:45.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这个窗帘有点透 所以刚才的我可都看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:49.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可恶 一副得意洋洋的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:51.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哎呀 真好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:54.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一想起西片刚才的举动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.77,0:13:59.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我早起一趟也算是值了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:01.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就为了这种事情早起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:03.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:11.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可恶的高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.62,0:14:13.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:23.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不觉得 两个人独处在安静的教室里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:26.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,会有一种整个世界只有我们两个人的感觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:32.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是能一直像这样 没有人来打扰就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:38.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那个…高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.31,0:14:40.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:44.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,难道说…对我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:48.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:52.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天天气真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.33,0:14:56.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的 为什么美奈一大早的就那么有精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.91,0:15:00.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么啊 这很普通啊 很普通的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:01.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.84,0:15:03.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不可以啊 早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.55,0:15:06.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是喊累的话 好运会溜走的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.47,0:15:07.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,电视里面是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.18,0:15:09.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你居然还相信那种东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:11.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那种事情怎么可能会发生嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:13.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:15.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有活力才好…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.23,0:15:16.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8s}吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:16.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,疼疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:18.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好疼啊 早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:20.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:23.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}好啦好啦 总之你们俩先笑一笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:25.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}来 笑一个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:26.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}来嘛来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:24.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你想说什么呢 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:28.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:33.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,话说回来 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:35.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,值日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:37.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我给忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:42.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:46.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,鬼脸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:49.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:50.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}知道知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:53.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我要怎么做才能赢高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:15:56.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:15:59.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.48,0:16:01.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,干什么呢 盯着镜子不放
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:02.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,中井
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.48,0:16:05.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在练习耍帅的姿势吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:07.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:11.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那么 是在做鬼脸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:14.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:15.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:16.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:21.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,话说回来 西片和高木同学关系真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:25.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,难道说 西片你对高木同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:30.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,想糊弄过去啊 看来是猜中了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.13,0:16:33.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片 你小子肯定是喜欢高木同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:39.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么啊西片 你那表情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:43.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真没想到 我还有这种才能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:46.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 那么开始上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:49.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,翻到36页
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:50.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,天助我也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.40,0:16:54.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,恰好是一旦发火就超级恐怖的田边老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:55.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你等着就被我的鬼脸逗笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:58.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,然后被老师臭骂一顿吧 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:09.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 真想早点让高木同学笑出声来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:11.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 我要忍住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:16.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在高木同学为了捉弄我来向我搭话前都要忍住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:19.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,人在打算捉弄别人的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:22.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,自己反而容易放松被捉弄的警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:25.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就要捉住那一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.19,0:17:27.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,来 放马过来吧高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:29.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,现在我可是浑身都是破绽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:31.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.74,0:17:32.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:35.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么啦高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:37.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:46.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:52.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:56.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,吵死了 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:17:58.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:18:00.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太恐怖了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:04.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:08.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我还以为你要干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:10.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真没意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:11.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:15.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,想做鬼脸的话 眉毛要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:19.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,然后把脸这样挤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:21.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:22.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没错没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:24.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 感觉不错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:27.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,比刚才好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:29.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么说好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:32.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,然后 像鸭子一样瘪嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:38.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,居然被想逗笑的对象指导我怎么逗人发笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:41.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,莫名地感到屈辱…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:43.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:45.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只要让高木同学笑出声来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:48.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,让她被老师骂了 我就赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:50.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:54.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很好 比刚才好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:57.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那你倒是笑一个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:19:00.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是你的侧脸对着我 我肯定会爆笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.95,0:19:03.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好嘞 接招吧高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.97,0:19:19.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:22.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:28.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的 上课给我认真点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:30.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的很对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:35.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的 笑得我肚子疼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.03,0:19:38.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,虽然她的确笑的很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:40.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,又被她摆了一道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.58,0:19:45.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:54.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是再惹田边老师生气就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.59,0:19:58.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,总之这节课不能再被高木同学捉弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:16.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,总算是往这边看了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.07,0:20:29.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,大眼瞪小眼 啊噗噗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.07,0:20:29.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs40}にらめっこ是日本的传统儿童游戏，两人面对面做鬼脸，先笑者输。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.07,0:20:29.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs40}玩的时候要唱这首歌，唱到「啊噗噗」的地方就不能露出表情或是做鬼脸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:35.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你那是什么表情啊 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.25,0:20:38.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片 你这小子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:43.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,每当我对高木同学心动的时候 总没好事发生
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——ed——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:18.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一百元
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.69,0:22:25.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天也好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.53,0:22:29.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以说 不可以把累挂在嘴边的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.62,0:22:31.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好运气会溜掉的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.62,0:22:32.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.55,0:22:45.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了 发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.72,0:22:49.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没什么 你们先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.72,0:22:50.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.55,0:22:52.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我有些累了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.76,0:22:55.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是说好运会溜走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.14,0:22:58.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.69,0:23:02.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,美奈 你脚下藏着什么东西呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.40,0:23:06.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那个 你们在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.62,0:23:18.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等 明明是我发现的一百元
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.17,0:23:21.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是贪心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.63,0:23:22.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,美奈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.17,0:23:25.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这个是代币
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.42,0:23:30.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因为我说了累字 所以变成代币了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.89,0:23:33.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你还在说那个事情吗
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.81,0:00:44.44,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:48.82,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:59.16,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:08.00,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}校庭で君のことを一番に見つけて今日は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.04,0:01:16.26,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて話しかけようか？ ちょっと考えるの楽しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.30,0:01:19.22,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風に揺らされるカーテン
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:24.60,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不意打ちに当たる日差し
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.68,0:01:28.48,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}眩しそうな顔を笑ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:32.40,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}照れて伏せちゃうのね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:40.49,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}憂鬱なテストも吹き飛ばせるような
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:48.79,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ねえ、二人で秘密の約束をしたいなって提案です
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:54.21,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.42,0:01:58.18,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:02:08.44,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPCH——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.81,0:00:44.44,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}会错意了也没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:48.82,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}和你一起就是幸福 这样想着却不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:59.16,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}弥漫在周围的那阵幽香 想在你的身边静静感受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:08.00,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}在校园的庭院 第一个发现你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.04,0:01:16.26,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}今天要和你说些什么呢 即便是想着这些也是一种乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.30,0:01:19.22,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}窗帘随风起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:24.60,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不经意地投入一束阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.68,0:01:28.48,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你那美丽的容颜笑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:32.40,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}羞得我抬不起头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:40.49,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}风儿喧嚣 似要吹散考试的忧郁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:48.79,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}呐 我想要和你一起 立下两人的秘密约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:54.21,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}会错意了也没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.42,0:01:58.18,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}和你一起就是幸福 这样想着却不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:02:08.44,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}弥漫在周围的那阵幽香 想在你的身边静静感受
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——EDJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:59.27,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ロマンティック　恋のアンテナは
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:04.99,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}嵐で　何処かへ飛んでいった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:09.49,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}噓でしょう　冷たくあしらった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:12.59,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}こしゃくなえくぼに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.59,0:21:16.50,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ちょっと　心が揺れてる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:27.43,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}本当は本気であたしを叱ってくれる大事な人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:36.14,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて 言いたらアイツは得意気になるから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.60,0:21:39.35,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}もう褒めたりしない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.52,0:21:44.82,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}退屈な運命に　飽き飽きしたね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.07,0:21:51.66,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}知らない言葉で　解き放して　ねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.66,0:21:57.12,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ダーリン　ダーリン　心の　扉を壊してよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:22:02.92,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}大切のことは目を見て　言って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:08.30,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}あなたとならば　この街を抜け出せる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.30,0:22:14.93,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}今すぐ連れ出して　My Sweet Sweet Darling
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——EDCH——
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:59.27,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}浪漫爱情的天线
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:04.99,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}狂风中不知飞向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:09.49,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}怎么会这样 对我这么冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:12.49,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}洋洋自得的酒窝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.49,0:21:16.50,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}稍微 有点心动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:27.43,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}其实 你是重视我而认真批评我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:36.14,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}如果这样说的话你一定会洋洋得意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.60,0:21:39.35,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}所以再也不会表扬你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.52,0:21:44.82,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}单调乏味的命运 我早已厌倦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.07,0:21:51.66,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}用未知的言语 解放我 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.66,0:21:57.12,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}Darling Darling 推倒封印心灵的大门吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:22:02.92,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}重要的事情就应该亲眼见证 亲口述说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:08.30,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}只要和你在一起 就能闯出这座小镇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.30,0:22:14.93,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}现在就带我走吧 My Sweet Sweet Darling
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——STAFF——
